'''基里巴斯駐外機構列表'''為[[大洋洲|大洋洲]]國家[[基里巴斯共和国|基里巴斯共和国]]派駐外國代表機構之列表，基里巴斯的外交代表机构较少，仅于2002年基于较多基里巴斯人在[[斐济|斐济]]侨居、学习之故在[[苏瓦|苏瓦]]设有一座大使馆。

2013年，基里巴斯曾经在[[台北|台北]]设有大使馆，2019年，因基里巴斯与[[中华民国|中华民国]]断交，其驻台大使馆也被关闭。<ref>[https://web.archive.org/web/20190419095601/https://sites.google.com/site/kiribatiembassyintaiwanroc/ Kiribati Embassy to Taiwan (R.O.C.)]</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2019/sep/20/taiwan-loses-second-ally-in-a-week-as-kiribati-switches-to-china |title=Taiwan loses second ally in a week as Kiribati switches to China {{!}} World news {{!}} The Guardian |accessdate=2020-09-06 |archive-date=2020-08-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200830155148/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2019/sep/20/taiwan-loses-second-ally-in-a-week-as-kiribati-switches-to-china |dead-url=no }}</ref>

